name: I.B.S.U model
description:
Incomplete But Still Uploading. Someone on 4chan wanted it so I'm uploading. It can do bags under the eyes well and has decent pupils. Not very colorful, but I like the style personally.

This model was made with a bit of training and merging. What was the process, don't remember don't care so it's being labeled as merged without an explanation.
